Ostrich Sans & Ostrich Sans Inline
==================================

[![Latest Release](https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/theleagueof/ostrich-sans?label=Download%20Release&logo=Github)](https://github.com/theleagueof/ostrich-sans/releases/latest)
[![All Releases](https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/theleagueof/ostrich-sans/total)](https://github.com/theleagueof/ostrich-sans/releases)
[![Fontship Build Status](https://img.shields.io/github/workflow/status/theleagueof/ostrich-sans/Fontship?label=Fontship&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)](https://github.com/theleagueof/ostrich-sans/actions?workflow=Fontship)

_by [Tyler Finck](https://www.tylerfinck.com/)_

A gorgeous modern sans-serif with a very long neck. With a whole slew of styles & weights:

- Dashed (thin)
- Rounded (medium)
- Ultra light
- Normal
- Bold (race track style double lines)
- Black
- Inline (with italics)
- Heavy (round)
